                Ziemices <certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Zi<supplied reason="lost">openis f.</supplied> eque<supplied reason="lost">s alae</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Thracum <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> turma <supplied reason="lost">Gai</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Vesperi hic situs est heres <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> ex</supplied> <lb n="4"/>testamento </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ζιμικένθισς <note>sic</note> Ζιωπῆν υἱός ἱππεὺ̣<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <lb n="2"/>εἴλης Θρᾳκῶν Σεβαστῆς τύρμης <lb n="3"/>Γαίω Ἑσπερίω <note>sic</note> ἐνθ&amp;lt;ά=Ε&amp;gt;δε κεῖται <lb n="4"/>ἐπ&amp;lt;οί=Υ&amp;gt;ησεν ὁ κληρονόμος <lb n="5"/>ἐγ διαθήκης 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1, 9. Buchstabe im thrak. Namen: nicht imitierbares Zeichen (durchgestrichenes F), offenbar zur Darstellung des griechischen Theta.</p>
